# 🤖 AI-Powered Workflow & Lead Automation Agent

Welcome to my second automation project! This repository contains a fully automated workflow built on **Make.com** (formerly Integromat). The core objective of this project is to demonstrate how modern businesses can leverage AI and automation to eliminate repetitive tasks, optimize client onboarding, and save hours of manual operation every week.

---

## 📑 Project Overview (نبذة عن المشروع)

هذا المشروع عبارة عن وكيل ذكاء اصطناعي ونظام أتمتة متكامل مخصص لإدارة البيانات الواردة بذكاء وتوفير الوقت والجهد على أصحاب الأعمال. يقوم النظام برصد البيانات، معالجتها وتحليلها عبر الذكاء الاصطناعي، ثم اتخاذ إجراءات فورية بناءً على المحتوى.

### 🔄 How the Workflow Works (آلية عمل الووركفلو)

1. **The Trigger (Google Forms):** The system instantly captures new submissions or inquiries from users.
2. **Data Logging (Google Sheets):** The incoming data is organized and logged into a central spreadsheet to ensure no leads are lost.
3. **AI Brain (Google Gemini AI):** Gemini analyzes the form inputs, extracts key details, filters useful insights, and drafts a highly professional, context-aware response.
4. **Action (Gmail):** The system automatically sends out the customized response as an email directly to the user without any human intervention.

